text: Ismail Al-Karaghouli (, born 15 June 1943) is an Iraqi wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Iraqi male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iraq Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Baghdad
